<item>
            <title>[SOLR-1259] scale() function doesn&apos;t work in multisegment indexes</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-1259</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;per yonik&apos;s comments in an email...&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;blockquote&gt;&lt;p&gt;Darn... another &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-1111&quot; title=&quot;fix FieldCache usage in Solr&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;SOLR-1111&quot;&gt;SOLR-1111&lt;/a&gt; related issue.  scale() will now only scale per-segment.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;

&lt;p&gt;...we either need to fix, or document prior to releasing 1.4&lt;/p&gt;</description>
